title: Are You Still Going to Chick- Fil-A
itunes:title: Are You Still Going to Chick- Fil-A
description:
3-22 Today on the show we opened up the phone lines after news hit headlines that Chick-Fil-A has donated millions dollars to anti-LGBTQ groups, so we wanted to see if members of the LGBTQ community will still be eating from the restaurant. Also, Charlagmagne for "Donkey of the Day" he gave the listeners a lesson how to properly kill a cockroach after a man tried to kill one but ended up shooting himself. Moreover, its Freaky Friday, so we wanted to see if any of our listeners like to be choked during sex, after Ari Lenox went on Angela's "Lip Service" and said that  she is totally against choking in sex.
